{"tid":2246171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨全國委員會向聯邦選舉委員會投訴Twitter審查涉向Biden陣營提供「非法實際政治捐獻」","createTime":"2020-10-16T23:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T00:29:35.000Z","uid":204533,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5df340837702e1a0785f8bb6d073febc163d21c6","tid":2246171,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T23:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The complaint, filed by the RNC on Friday and obtained exclusively by Fox News, states that the RNC &ldquo;believes that Twitter has violated FECA and the Commission&rsquo;s Regulations by making corporate in-kind contributions to Biden for President.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe RNC, in its complaint, said Twitter &ldquo;is a partisan actor, run by partisan Democrats&rdquo; and is &ldquo;<strong><span class=\"red\">using its corporate resources to provide active support for Joe Biden&rsquo;s campaign in violation of federal law,</span></strong>&rdquo; and <strong><span class=\"red\">demanded the FEC &ldquo;conduct an immediate investigation&rdquo; into Twitter&rsquo;s &ldquo;illegal in-kind contributions to the Biden campaign,&rdquo; and &ldquo;<span class=\"xx-large\">impose the maximum penalty allowed under the law.&rdquo;</span></span></strong><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/rnc-fec-twitter-complaint-claims-company-made-illegal-in-kind-contribution-biden-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Frnc-fec-twitter-complaint-claims-company-made-illegal-in-kind-contribution-biden-campaign&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haox6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=c15dbd85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Frnc-fec-twitter-complaint-claims-company-made-illegal-in-kind-contribution-biden-campaign&h=91f23560\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/rnc-fec-twitter-complaint-claims-company-made-illegal-in-kind-contribution-biden-ca